Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:06.58,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn大赦黑体 DemiBold\fs40\c&H000000&\t(0,5000,\fs45)\fad(0,2000)\be1\move(1336,535,1381,502,0,4963)}獲邀參加生存遊戲對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:06.58,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn大赦黑体 DemiBold\fs40\c&H000000&\t(0,5000,\fs45)\fad(0,2000)\be1\move(575,1013,537,1031,0,4963)}獲許可後辦的露營
